and rights

02:13.265 --> 02:16.669
becomes a serious political
and social concern?

02:16.701 --> 02:20.605
In what year will there be
an app or computer program

02:20.639 --> 02:24.176
<i>or a device
that you not only love</i>

02:24.208 --> 02:25.910
<i>but that possibly,
within the realm</i>

02:25.944 --> 02:32.017
of believability might
actually love ...you ...back?

02:32.050 --> 02:35.354
When we don't just have
relationships to technology,

02:35.386 --> 02:40.158
but relationships
with technology?

02:40.192 --> 02:41.826
Here's to us.

02:41.860 --> 02:42.994
[kisses]

02:50.002 --> 02:52.037
<i>How do you define love?</i>

02:52.069 --> 02:54.973
She likes it when I rub
her head in order to kiss her.

02:55.006 --> 02:58.611
<i>Does it have to be mutual
amongst consenting adults</i>

02:58.643 --> 03:00.813
<i>or is it an emotion
belonging to one individual?</i>

03:00.845 --> 03:02.647
- Oh, you want a kiss?
- All right.

03:02.681 --> 03:04.183
I love you too.

03:04.216 --> 03:07.186
<i>Harold freely admits
that he has fallen in love</i>

03:07.218 --> 03:08.353
<i>with a video game.</i>

03:08.386 --> 03:10.788
- So Harold?
- Yeah.

03:10.821 --> 03:12.157
- Hello.
- Mm-hmm.

